Package business

Class Module

java.lang.Object
business.Module
All Implemented Interfaces:
IModule
public class Module
extends java.lang.Object
implements IModule
Represents an academic module within the system. This class handles the storage and manipulation of module data including module name, code, academic year, and associated courses.

The class provides functionality for:

  • Creating and managing module information
  • JSON serialisation and deserialisation
  • Filtering and searching modules
  • Course association management
